CONTEXT UnionTypeMismatchCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT UnionTypeMismatchCheck
{+ Test that union fails when operands have different signatures.
   This verifies the type checker correctly rejects r[A*B] \/ s[B*C] due to signature mismatch. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testUnionFail: result = r \/ s

ENDCONTEXT
